data.description: Investor's Dream! 3 bedroom, 2 bath handyman special is your canvas for transformation. Sprawling 100x200 lot has potential for expansion or renovation. The home features a cozy layout with room to customize and create your ideal living space.  Out side, an in ground pool offers great recreational space.  This property is a blank slate waiting for your vision to turn it into a gem.  With some TLC, it can become a standout in a charming neighborhood.  Don't miss the opportunityto bring this house back to life and make it your own.
